    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:1.3",
          "pli": "Tatra kho bhagavā … pe … etadavoca: ",
          "en": "There the Buddha … said: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:2.1",
          "pli": "“Appamidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussānaṃ āyu. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, the life span of humans is short. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:2.2",
          "pli": "Gamanīyo samparāyo, kattabbaṃ kusalaṃ, caritabbaṃ brahmacariyaṃ. ",
          "en": "You must go to the next life. So you should do what is skillful, you should practice the spiritual life. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:2.3",
          "pli": "Natthi jātassa amaraṇaṃ. ",
          "en": "No-one born is immortal. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:2.4",
          "pli": "Yo, bhikkhave, ciraṃ jīvati, so vassasataṃ appaṃ vā bhiyyo”ti. ",
          "en": "A long life is a hundred years or a little more.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:3.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:4.1",
          "pli": "“Nāccayanti ahorattā, ",
          "en": "“The days and nights don’t rush by, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:4.2",
          "pli": "Jīvitaṃ nūparujjhati; ",
          "en": "and life isn’t cut short. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:4.3",
          "pli": "Āyu anupariyāyati maccānaṃ, ",
          "en": "The life of mortals keeps rolling on, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:4.4",
          "pli": "Nemīva rathakubbaran”ti. ",
          "en": "like a chariot’s rim around the hub.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:5.1",
          "pli": "“Accayanti ahorattā, ",
          "en": "“The days and nights rush by, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:5.2",
          "pli": "jīvitaṃ uparujjhati; ",
          "en": "and then life is cut short. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:5.3",
          "pli": "Āyu khīyati maccānaṃ, ",
          "en": "The life of mortals wastes away, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:5.4",
          "pli": "kunnadīnaṃva odakan”ti. ",
          "en": "like the water in tiny streams.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:6.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. ",
          "en": "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:6.2",
          "pli": "Paṭhamo vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:7.1",
          "pli": "Tapokammañca nāgo ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:7.2",
          "pli": "subhaṃ pāsena te duve; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:7.3",
          "pli": "Sappo supati nandanaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn4.10:7.4",
          "pli": "āyunā apare duveti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
